302 mai naam rahe se,
Maare aval kaam rahe se

Chal bukal maarkay

Laage minute ka chotha hisa 
Dhar dyu chaati paad ke

The song captures her love, fear, and pain of leaving the house where she grew up. She remembers small fights, shared laughter, and the comfort of seeing her parents every day. Before starting her new life, she makes emotional requests to her brother and sister, showing how strongly she is connected to her family. Rishtey beautifully reflects love, memories, and the strength it takes to move forward while keeping family close to the heart.

#TheReviewPoint


Rocking Star Yash is back, and this time it‚Äôs not about mass hysteria or KGF-style nostalgia.
The TOXIC teaser is a calculated, controlled, and deeply unsettling cinematic statement that feels more like a warning than a promotion.

In this video, we break down TOXIC from a pure movie critic‚Äôs perspective ‚Äî focusing on visual grammar, sound design, character psychology, director Geethu Mohandas‚Äô intent, and why this teaser has already started shaking the industry.

Watch till the end to understand:
* Why TOXIC is not trying to please everyone
* How Yash is repositioning himself post-KGF
* Why silence in this teaser is louder than BGM
* What the teaser hides ‚Äî and why that matters

snippet.title: Teri Dulhan Sajaoongi | Barsaat | Alka Yagnik | Kailash Khair | Nadeem Shravan
snippet.description:
‚ÄúTeri Dulhan Sajaoongi‚Äù is a soulful romantic track from the film Barsaat, beautifully sung by Alka Yagnik and Kailash Kher. Composed by the legendary duo Nadeem‚ÄìShravan, the song captures pure love, devotion, and the heartfelt promise of a bride preparing herself for her beloved.

Movie: a sublime love story- Barsaat (2005)
Featuring: Bobby Deol, Priyanka Chopra, and Bipasha Basu
Song: Saajan Saajan Teri Dulhan Sajaoongi 
Singers: Alka Yagnik, Kailash Kher
Music: Nadeem Shravan
Lyrics: Sameer
Produced & Director: Suneel Darshan
Production : Shree Krishna International
Music Lable: Shree Krishna Audio


Song Lyrics:

Hazaro Manzilein Hogi Hazaro Karwaa Honge
Nigaahein Humko Dhundegi Na Jaane Hum Kaha Honge
Saajan Saajan Saajan Mere Saajan Mere Saajan
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi Teri Dulhan Sajaungi
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi
Wada Diya Tujhe Jo Bhi Wada Diya Tujhe Main
Wo Wada Nibhaungi Main Woh Wada Nibhaaungi
Saajan Saajan Saajan Mere Saajan Mere Saajan
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi Teri Dulhan Sajaungi
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi Teri Dulhan Sajaungi

Jhilmil Sitaaro Ki Chaiyya Lungi Mein Teri Balaiyaa
Jhilmil Sitaaro Ki Chaiyya Lungi Mein Teri Balaiyaa
Itna Tujhe Pyaar Dungi Ye Jindagi Waar Dungi
Muskurati Hain Najar Dil Tadap Ke Rota Hai
Aur Chot Jab Lagti Hain Uff To Dard Bada Hota
Saajan Saajan Saajan Mere Saajan Mere Saajan
Dard Saare Uthaungi Dard Saare Uthaungi
Saajan Saajan Saajan Mere Saajan Mere Saajan
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi Teri Dulhan Sajaungi
Teri Dulhan Sajaungi Teri Dulhan Sajaungi

Hum Haste Hain Toh Unhe Lagta Hai
Hume Aadaat Hai Muskuraane Ki
Par Wo Nadaan Itna Bhi Nahi Samajhte

Since launching a string of hits beginning in 2009, Bruno has sold over 150 million records worldwide, making him one of the best-selling artists of all time. Beyond his work as a soloist, Bruno is a member of the duo Silk Sonic with Anderson .Paak. In addition to his 35 Billboard Hot 100 hits, including nine number one singles, Bruno is the recipient of 16 GRAMMY¬Æ Awards (including ‚ÄúAlbum of the Year‚Äù for 24K Magic), 14 American Music Awards, and seven MTV Video Music Awards. His 24K Magic World Tour was among the highest-grossing tours in history, and within the top ten highest-grossing of the 2010s.

By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. ‚Äî In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story shifts toward legacy, duty, and the consequences of survival as Shuri carries the weight of a world that has taken everything from her. Having lost her family, her king, and her past, she steps fully into her role not just as Black Panther, but as a leader navigating the fragile balance between nations shaped by grief and power. Her path intersects with Talokan, where Namor stands as a reminder that kings are defined by the burdens they accept, not the battles they fight. As Wakanda looks beyond its borders, a historic meeting finally comes to pass with the Fantastic Four, signaling alliances forged across generations and timelines. The trailer positions these converging forces as essential players in the coming conflict, framing Avengers: Doomsday as a story about responsibility inherited, choices made in silence, and the fragile unity required to prevent the collapse of everything that remains.

snippet.title: AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY (2026) | Wakandans & Fantastic 4 Trailer | Marvel Comics | Concept
snippet.description:
#Marvel #Avengers #Avengersdoomsday #ChrisEvans #Robertdowneyjr
 
üé• Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Avengers: Doomsday Trailer unleashes a massive turning point for the Marvel Cinematic Universe, with shocking footage rumored from the Doomsday trailer leak, including the intense Wakanda Doomsday trailer and a leaked Wakanda teaser that hints at global fallout. As the threat escalates, the Doomsday X-Men trailer, Fantastic Four teaser, and multiple versions like Doomsday Trailer 4 and Doomsday Teaser 4 suggest the MCU is colliding into one catastrophic event. With whispers of leaked footage, surprise returns, and Wakanda at the center of the chaos, Doomsday promises multiversal consequences, powerful alliances, and the beginning of Marvel‚Äôs darkest chapter yet.

The inspiration behind this video:
The internet is breaking again! In this video, we break down the shocking Avengers Doomsday trailer leak that reveals a massive crossover event between Wakanda and the Fantastic Four. Known online as the Doomsday trailer 4, this footage features Shuri delivering a chilling monologue about "preparing for the afterlife" as she unites with Namor to defend Earth. We analyze every frame of this doomsday wakanda trailer, including the hilarious first interaction between M'Baku and The Thing, and what this "unlikely team-up" means for the plot of the Avengers Doomsday movie.

We also connect this new footage to the previous Doomsday X Men trailer leak, which showed Cyclops and Magneto making their final stand. As Marvel Studios ramps up marketing for Avengers 2026, it is clear that Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom is waging war on every corner of the multiverse. We discuss how these Doomsday teaser clips‚Äîfrom the Doomsday Fantastic Four teaser to the Wakandan invasion‚Äîpaint a terrifying picture of the Doctor Doom MCU variant. Is this truly a Doctor Doom movie where the villain wins, forcing the surviving heroes to retreat into Secret Wars?

Finally, we look ahead to the Avengers Doomsday official trailer release and what to expect from Marvel Phase 6. We theorize on why Marvel is leaking these Doomsday trailer spots during the Avatar run and whether the official Avengers Doomsday marvel trailer will finally show RDJ in the full armor. From the wakanda trailer leak details to the full Avengers Doomsday cast breakdown, this is your ultimate guide to the end of the Marvel Cinematic Universe as we know it.

snippet.description:
Will TOXIC be able  to break  Dhurandhar's Records at Box Office ?
Well, Well, well...... It doesn't look like that !! Yash is indeed having that Aura, that Swag you can't MISS.. But the action choreography and the special effects department have miserably failed at it :(
Being a Yash's Fan, I didn't find it good, because of the soft po*n scenes in the teaser. Those Slow motions were irritating me the whole time !! 
But, still lets HOPE for it !!
